We can add custom fields to an issue. Would liek to be able to ad custom field to a comment. This would allow a catagory type drop down when adding a comment.

{panel:bgColor=#e7f4fa}
  *NOTE:* This suggestion is for *JIRA Server*. Using *JIRA Cloud*? [See the corresponding suggestion|http://jira.atlassian.com/browse/JRACLOUD-1535].
  {panel}

We should allow a PDF version of each issue, so that issues can be sent electronically, or printed in a nicer format.

Perhaps we can use HTML2PDF or make the underlying page use velocity, which we can adapt to make PDFs.

{panel:bgColor=#e7f4fa}
  *NOTE:* This suggestion is for *JIRA Server*. Using *JIRA Cloud*? [See the corresponding suggestion|http://jira.atlassian.com/browse/JRACLOUD-1522].
  {panel}

It would be nice to modify the notification scheme and enable an all commenters option. So anyone who comments on an issue is notified of any modifications to it, for example, without them having to explicitly watch it.

